      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>chicken breast</strong> <strong>strips </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour </strong>to a plate and a splash of <strong>milk </strong>to a small bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>to another plate with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>garam masala </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your <strong>curry powder </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and mix together (this will make your breadcrumbs golden!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1665138684994-x200.jpg",
