            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season the <strong>chicken pieces </strong>generously with <strong>salt</strong>, then coat them in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add them to the <strong>milk </strong>and finally press them into the <strong>breadcrumbs </strong>firmly to coat evenly</p><p>Add the <strong>breaded chicken nuggets </strong>to a separate baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 15-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and golden – these are your <strong>spiced chicken nuggets</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1665138688771-x200.jpg",
