      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken and chips are cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
