    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
