    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the beans have thickened, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min or until starting to wilt – these are your <strong>masala saag beans</strong></p>",
